<h4 class="pdoc-member-header" id="NetworkLoadBalancerArgs-dropInvalidHeaderFields">
<a class="pdoc-child-name" href="https://github.com/pulumi/pulumi-awsx/blob/43b8dabc0ec1e5187bf63e107bf06ee54021a1a7/sdk/nodejs/lb/networkLoadBalancer.ts#L116">property <b>dropInvalidHeaderFields</b></a>

Elastic Load Balancing requires that message header names contain only alphanumeric characters and hyphens. Only valid for Load Balancers of type `application`.
